{
  "texts": [
    "The study explored the fusion of MRI with cross-sectional biomarkers such as demographic and cognitive scores.",
    "SHAP was employed to enhance interpretability for domain experts.",
    "Results demonstrated the framework's robustness, achieving 96% accuracy, 99% precision, 92% recall, and a 96% AUC.",
    "The fusion of MRI with demographic features enhanced stability, and the explainability module provided valuable insights by accurately identifying brain regions relevant to AD diagnoses.In summary, studies combining numeric, categorical, and image data for AD classification utilise diverse machine learning models.",
    "XAI methods like SHAP and LIME enhance interpretability, shedding light on influential features."
  ]
}